high_descs: Turn right and walk to the sink.
Open the cabinet below the left sink basin and take out the ladle, then close the cabinet.
Walk away slightly backwards from the cabinet.
Put the ladle in the left sink basin, rinse it off, and take it out of the sink.
Walk away slightly backwards from the sink.
Put the ladle in the cabinet below the right sink basin, between the two salt containers, then close the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned ladle in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn to your right and go to the sink across from you.
Pull put the ladle from the cabinet under the small, left sink.
Step back from the cabinet, and step forward to the sink.
Place the ladle in the small right sink, turn the water on, rinse the ladle off, turn the water off, then remove the ladle from the sink.
Move away from the sink and over to your right so that you are in front of the larger sink on the right.
Place the ladle in the lower cabinet, under the large sink on the right.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean ladle in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right and cross the room to face the sink.
Open the cabinet below the sink on the left and take the ladle out.
Move back and face the sink again.
Put the ladle in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick the ladle up again.
Back up and face the cabinet under the sink on the right.
Open the cabinet below the sink on the right and put the ladle in it and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean ladle in the cabinet.
